README.md

Awesome

   A collection of awesome [http://www.refinerycms.com/]Refinery CMS
   extensions, resources and shiny things.

Frontoffice extensions

     * [https://github.com/unixcharles/refinerycms-copywriting]refinerycms
       -copywriting - Write once, display at the infinite
     * [https://github.com/refinerycms-contrib/refinerycms-elasticsearch]r
       efinerycms-elasticsearch - Fulltext search with
       [https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch-ruby]Elasticsearch
     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/refinerycms-image-slideshows]refineryc
       ms-image-slideshows - Display slideshows
     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/refinerycms-jobs]refinerycms-jobs -
       Job Posting and Job Applications
     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/refinerycms-products]refinerycms-produ
       cts - Display products
     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/refinerycms-retailers]refinerycms-reta
       ilers - Display retailers
     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/refinerycms-teams]refinerycms-teams -
       Display teams
     * [https://github.com/anitagraham/refinerycms-testimonials]refinerycm
       s-testimonials - Manage and display testimonials
     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/refinerycms-videos]refinerycms-videos
       - Basic display of Youtube videos

Backoffice extensions

     * [https://github.com/jfalameda/refinerycms-dynamicfields]refinerycms
       -dynamicfields - Create models dynamically and attach them to pages
     * [https://github.com/anitagraham/refinerycms-page-resources]refinery
       cms-page-resources - Attach resources (files) to a Page
     * [https://github.com/rabid/refinerycms-redactor]refinerycms-redactor
       - WYSIWYG editor with [https://imperavi.com/redactor/]Redactor
     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/refinerycms-resource-categories]refine
       rycms-resource-categories - Categorize resources
     * [https://github.com/cleverlemming/refinerycms-snoods]refinerycms-sn
       oods - Creating download pages and sending leads to Salesforce
     * [https://github.com/ghoppe/refinerycms-tinymce]refinerycms-tinymce
       - TinyMCE Visual Editing

Solidus e-commerce + Refinery extensions

     * [https://github.com/refinerycms-contrib/solidus-refinery-authentica
       tion]solidus-refinery-authentication - Shared auth between Solidus
       and Refinery

Spree e-commerce + Refinery extensions

     * [https://github.com/bisscomm/spree_refinery_resources]spree_refiner
       y_resources - Attach resources (files) to a Spree::Product
     * [https://github.com/refinerycms-contrib/spree-refinery-authenticati
       on]spree-refinery-authentication - Shared auth between Spree and
       Refinery

Refinery team extensions

Main project

     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms/tree/master/core]Core
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms/tree/master/images]Images
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms/tree/master/pages]Pages
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms/tree/master/resources]Reso
       urces

Frontoffice extensions

     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-authentication-devise]refi
       nerycms-authentication-devise - Devise based authentication
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-blog]refinerycms-blog -
       Blog (more features than
       [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-news]refinerycms-news)
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-inquiries]refinerycms-inqu
       iries - Send contact forms
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-news]refinerycms-news -
       Basic display of news
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-portfolio]refinerycms-porf
       olio - Display portfolio images
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-search]refinerycms-search
       - Fulltext search with
       [https://github.com/dougal/acts_as_indexed]ActAsIndexed

Backoffice extensions

     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-page-images]refinerycms-pa
       ge-images - Attach images to a Page
     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-settings]refinerycms-setti
       ngs - Change settings in the backoffice

Developer tools

     * [https://github.com/refinery/refinerycms-forms]Forms
